otp_autofill.description: Android implementation of OTP autofill with using User Consent API and Retriever API. Add possibility to receive OTP code from another input.

bottom_sheet.description: Flexible bottom sheet with the ability to scroll content even without a list.

push_notification.description: Library for implementing push notifications. The module contains the main work with push notifications.

swipe_refresh.description: Set of widgets provides make refresh by using pull down gesture.
